{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1047,"text":"Over the next five minutes,"},{"time":2390,"text":"my intention is to transform\nyour relationship with sound."},{"time":6063,"text":"Let me start with the observation"},{"time":7662,"text":"that most of the sound\naround us is accidental;"},{"time":9904,"text":"much of it is unpleasant. (Traffic noise)"},{"time":12042,"text":"We stand on street corners,\nshouting over noise like this,"},{"time":14829,"text":"pretending it doesn't exist."},{"time":16229,"text":"This habit of suppressing sound has meant"},{"time":18230,"text":"that our relationship with sound\nhas become largely unconscious."}]},{"cues":[{"time":21602,"text":"There are four major ways\nsound is affecting you all the time,"},{"time":24603,"text":"and I'd like to raise them\nin your consciousness today."},{"time":27222,"text":"The first is physiological."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28867,"text":"(Alarm clocks ring)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":31761,"text":"Sorry about that."},{"time":32941,"text":"I just gave you a shot of cortisol,\nyour fight-flight hormone."},{"time":35888,"text":"Sounds are affecting\nyour hormone secretions all the time,"},{"time":38666,"text":"but also your breathing, heart rate --\nwhich I just also did --"},{"time":41930,"text":"and your brainwaves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":43379,"text":"It's not just unpleasant sounds\nlike that that do it."},{"time":45906,"text":"This is surf. (Ocean waves)"},{"time":47239,"text":"It has the frequency of roughly\n12 cycles per minute."},{"time":49756,"text":"Most people find that very soothing,"},{"time":51529,"text":"and, interestingly, 12 cycles per minute\nis roughly the frequency"},{"time":54649,"text":"of the breathing of a sleeping human,"},{"time":56452,"text":"so there is a deep resonance\nwith being at rest."},{"time":58793,"text":"We also associate it\nwith being stress-free and on holiday."}]},{"cues":[{"time":62122,"text":"The second way in which sound\naffects you is psychological."},{"time":65489,"text":"Music is the most powerful form\nof sound that we know"},{"time":67998,"text":"that affects our emotional state.\n(Albinoni's Adagio)"},{"time":70531,"text":"This is guaranteed to make most of you\nfeel pretty sad if I leave it on."},{"time":74000,"text":"Music is not the only kind of sound,\nhowever, which affects your emotions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":77501,"text":"Natural sound can do that, too."},{"time":79359,"text":"Birdsong, for example, is a sound\nwhich most people find reassuring."},{"time":83000,"text":"There's a reason:\nover hundreds of thousands of years"},{"time":85535,"text":"we've learned that when the birds\nare singing, things are safe."},{"time":88528,"text":"It's when they stop\nyou need to be worried."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90557,"text":"The third way in which\nsound affects you is cognitively."},{"time":93209,"text":"You can't understand two people\ntalking at once (Voice-over)"},{"time":96070,"text":"or in this case, one person talking twice."},{"time":98139,"text":"You have to choose which me\nyou're going to listen to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":100717,"text":"We have a very small amount of bandwidth\nfor processing auditory input,"},{"time":104105,"text":"which is why noise like this ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":105689,"text":"(Office noise)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":106728,"text":"is extremely damaging for productivity."},{"time":108638,"text":"If you have to work\nin an open-plan office like this,"},{"time":111171,"text":"your productivity is greatly reduced."},{"time":113000,"text":"And whatever number you're thinking of,\nit probably isn't as bad as this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":116501,"text":"[Open-plan offices productivity down 66%]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":120074,"text":"You are one-third as productive\nin open-plan offices as in quiet rooms."},{"time":123715,"text":"I have a tip for you:"},{"time":124890,"text":"if you work in spaces like that,\ncarry headphones with you,"},{"time":127699,"text":"with a soothing sound like birdsong."},{"time":129461,"text":"Put them on, and your productivity\ngoes back up to triple what it would be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133069,"text":"The fourth way in which\nsound affects us is behaviorally."},{"time":136323,"text":"With all that other stuff going on,"},{"time":138032,"text":"it would be amazing\nif our behavior didn't change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":140419,"text":"(Techno music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":141452,"text":"So ask yourself: Is this person\never going to drive"},{"time":143895,"text":"at a steady 28 miles per hour?"},{"time":145393,"text":"I don't think so."},{"time":146568,"text":"At the simplest, you move\naway from unpleasant sound"},{"time":149501,"text":"and towards pleasant sounds."},{"time":150960,"text":"So if I were to play this ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":152421,"text":"(Jackhammer)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":153662,"text":"for more than a few seconds,\nyou'd feel uncomfortable;"},{"time":156258,"text":"for more than a few minutes,\nyou'd be leaving the room in droves."},{"time":159347,"text":"For people who can't get away\nfrom noise like that,"},{"time":161775,"text":"it's extremely damaging for their health."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163776,"text":"And that's not the only thing\nthat bad sound damages."},{"time":166309,"text":"Most retail sound is inappropriate\nand accidental, even hostile,"},{"time":169628,"text":"and it has a dramatic effect on sales."},{"time":171752,"text":"For you retailers, you may want\nto look away before I show this slide."}]},{"cues":[{"time":175164,"text":"[Inappropriate retail soundscapes\nsales down 28%]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":177520,"text":"They're losing up to 30 percent\nof their business"},{"time":179949,"text":"with people leaving shops faster,\nor just turning around at the door."},{"time":183231,"text":"We've all done it, left the area,"},{"time":184848,"text":"because the sound in there is so dreadful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186882,"text":"I want to spend just a moment\ntalking about the model we've developed,"},{"time":190249,"text":"which allows us to start at the top\nand look at the drivers of sound,"},{"time":193537,"text":"analyze the soundscape"},{"time":194728,"text":"and then predict the four outcomes\nI just talked about."},{"time":197369,"text":"Or start at the bottom\nand say what outcomes we want,"},{"time":200263,"text":"and then design a soundscape\nto have a desired effect."},{"time":202852,"text":"At last we've got\nsome science we can apply."},{"time":204977,"text":"And we're in the business\nof designing soundscapes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":207412,"text":"Just a word on music."},{"time":208713,"text":"Music is the most powerful sound there is,\noften inappropriately deployed."},{"time":212384,"text":"It's powerful for two reasons:"},{"time":213893,"text":"you recognize it fast,\nand you associate it very powerfully."},{"time":217000,"text":"I'll give you two examples."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218618,"text":"(First chord of \"A Hard Day's Night\")"}]},{"cues":[{"time":220512,"text":"Most of you recognize that immediately."},{"time":222442,"text":"The younger, maybe not."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223617,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":224849,"text":"(First notes of \"Jaws\" theme)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":226269,"text":"Most of you associate that with something!"},{"time":228376,"text":"Now, those are one-second\nsamples of music."},{"time":230525,"text":"Music is very powerful,"},{"time":231701,"text":"and unfortunately, it's veneering\ncommercial spaces, often inappropriately."},{"time":235587,"text":"I hope that's going to change\nover the next few years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":238517,"text":"Let me talk about brands for a moment,\nsince some of you run brands."},{"time":241737,"text":"Every brand is out there\nmaking sound right now."},{"time":244025,"text":"There are eight expressions of a brand\nin sound; they're all important."},{"time":247406,"text":"And every brand needs to have\nguidelines at the center."},{"time":250050,"text":"I'm glad to say\nthat is starting to happen now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252333,"text":"(Intel ad jingle)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":253935,"text":"You all recognize that one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":255524,"text":"(Nokia ringtone)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":256555,"text":"This is the most-played tune\nin the world today --"},{"time":259071,"text":"1.8 billion times a day,\nthat tune is played."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261303,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":262383,"text":"And it cost Nokia absolutely nothing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264765,"text":"I'll leave you with four golden rules,\nfor those of you who run businesses,"},{"time":268341,"text":"for commercial sound."},{"time":269521,"text":"First, make it congruent,"},{"time":271000,"text":"pointing in the same direction\nas your visual communication."},{"time":274151,"text":"That increases impact\nby over 1,100 percent."},{"time":276809,"text":"If your sound is pointing\nthe opposite direction, incongruent,"},{"time":280000,"text":"you reduce impact by 86 percent."},{"time":282000,"text":"That's an order of magnitude, up or down."},{"time":284710,"text":"This is important."},{"time":286218,"text":"Secondly, make it appropriate\nto the situation."},{"time":289000,"text":"Thirdly, make it valuable."},{"time":290281,"text":"Give people something with the sound,\ndon't just bombard them with stuff."},{"time":293773,"text":"Finally, test and test it again."},{"time":295356,"text":"Sound is complex; there are many\ncountervailing influences."},{"time":298164,"text":"It can be a bit like a bowl of spaghetti:"},{"time":300165,"text":"sometimes you just have to eat it\nand see what happens."}]},{"cues":[{"time":302821,"text":"So I hope this talk has raised sound\nin your consciousness."},{"time":305634,"text":"If you're listening consciously,"},{"time":307219,"text":"you can take control\nof the sound around you."},{"time":309355,"text":"It's good for your health\nand for your productivity."},{"time":312003,"text":"If we all do that, we move to a state"},{"time":313820,"text":"that I like to think will be\nsound living in the world."},{"time":316429,"text":"I'll leave you with more birdsong.\n(Birds chirping)"},{"time":318850,"text":"I recommend at least five minutes\na day, but there's no maximum dose."}]},{"cues":[{"time":322159,"text":"Thank you for lending me your ears today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":324215,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}